'''Vox''' (often stylized as '''VOX''') is a [[list of political parties in Spain|political party in Spain]] founded on 17 December 2013, by former members of the [[People's Party (Spain)|People's Party]] (PP). The party is described variously as [[Right-wing politics|right-wing]],<ref>
